# Keyboard Shortcut Help Sync

When adding, removing, or changing keyboard and mouse shortcuts, update the in-app Help content in the same change.

## Required updates

- Update the Help text shown by `ShowKeyboardShortcuts()`.
- Keep shortcut descriptions accurate, including modifier keys and step sizes.
- If behavior changes from the current default, update wording so users can discover the new behavior.

## PR/check checklist

- New/changed shortcut present in Help.
- Old shortcut wording removed or corrected.
- Shortcut wording matches actual key handling in code.

## Example

- If `Ctrl+Up` and `Ctrl+Down` are added for zoom, Help must list both and note the 10% step.
